"Now, in the event that the coach had slowed down abruptly, the laws of physics would obviously be valid.
In the same way as in an urban bus or in a tram.
The carrier must manage the safety of the stewards by internal requirements," he said and also felt that, from the point of view of the law, the problem had not been resolved.
Janura is ready to abolish these services
Student Agency is the only coach carrier to offer stewards services.
He hired two hundred.
