Janaura refused to allow the two seats reserved for the stewards' rests to have been sold.
"In the case of long-distance lines, it is not possible to reserve these seats, they are blocked."
The company intends to file a complaint against the driver of the truck.
In order to compensate the girl's family, the agency will not wait for the court's judgement, but as far as the financial compensation is concerned, it also relies on the guilty party.
An amendment to the law?
Not in sight
An amendment to the law, which has been being drafted for more than a year, by a group of 30 experts from the Ministry of Transport, could clarify the movements of stewards on board the coach.
"Now, it did not reach any conclusion on this point.
To tell the truth, she is not too interested in buses, but rather in the system of points, at the maximum speed on the motorway and the use of the mobile phone while driving,' says expert Hoon.
"The Ministry of Transport does not regard the activity of stewards as something that would fundamentally endanger passenger safety," concluded spokesman Hanzelka, pointing out that the control of coach security is under the power of the police and the office for occupational safety.
